name: Get all transactions
fullName: Fraud Detection API: Get all transactions

steps.name: When I send a GET request to "/api/fraud-detection/"
Then the response status code should be 200
And the response should contain "transactions"
And the response should contain "transaction_id"
And the response should contain "user_id"
And the response should contain "amount"
And the response should contain "currency"
And the response should contain "location"
And the response should contain "merchant_id"
And the response should contain "timestamp"
And the response should contain "ip_address"
And the response should contain "fraud_status"
And the response should contain "fraud_score"
And the response should contain "alerts"
